crime. 
</P>
<P>
 GRAYCE W. WEBSTER, Laguna Beach 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 The judge who sentenced Ellie Nesler to 10 years in prison doesn't see the big 
picture. I'm sure he's pleased with himself for sticking resolutely to the 
