 * Movie or miniseries: "The Positively True Adventures of the Alleged Texas 
Cheerleader-Murdering Mom," HBO. 
</P>
<P>
 * Actor, comedy: Rip Torn, "The Larry Sanders Show," HBO. 
</P>
<P>
 * Actress, comedy: Wendie Malick, "Dream On," HBO. 
</P>
<P>
 * Actor, dramatic series: Gary Oldman, "Fallen Angels: Dead End for Delia," 
